Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: j01.scroller
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: JQuery and j01.jsonrpc based pagination for Zope 3
Home-page: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/j01.scroller
Author: Roger Ineichen, Projekt01 GmbH
Author-email: dev@projekt01.ch
License: ZPL 2.1
Description: ======
        README
        ======
        
        This package contains an infinite scroller based on batch data like known from
        the j01.pager package.
        
        
        =======
        CHANGES
        =======
        
        1.0.0 (2015-03-17)
        ------------------
        
        - support new j01.jsonrpc j01.proxy.js implementation
        
        - make scroller work with element as context and use the element as scroll
          container. Support scroller data loading based on javascript libraries.
        
        - implemented support for nanoscroller
        
        - implemented support for m custom scroller (recommended)
        
        
        0.5.0 (2013-01-21)
        ------------------
        
        - initial release
        
